.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-PPM-KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-ppm-kurtosis \- FEAT-2847 channel-fee-ppm-kurtosis
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-ppm-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the excess kurtosis of fee_proportional_millionths across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2847).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_ppm_kurtosis\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
